text: Oikonomos Football Club () is a Greek football club, based in Tsaritsani, Larissa regional unit. The association was founded in 1953. In 2011, they were promoted to the Football League 2 for the first time in history after becoming champions of the 2010–11 Delta Ethniki. ==Honours== ===Domestic=== ** Delta Ethniki champions: 1 *** 2010–11 ** Larissa FCA Champions: 2 *** 2009–10, 2017–18 ** Larissa FCA Cup Winners: 1 *** 2017–18 ==References== ==External links== *Official website Category:Football clubs in Thessaly Category:1953 establishments in Greece Category:Larissa (regional unit)
